Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:03.27,Station,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Bubaigawara Station
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.20,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mashima-senpai going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.33,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Cram school?  Part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.67,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is he meeting with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.46,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.25,society,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cultural Center
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:38.01,obviously,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Shiranami \NKaruta \NSociety \NPractice \NRoom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:37.08,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,More karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:50.07,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:53.13,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Verse 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:53.13,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}As My \NLove \NFirst\N Came
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.61,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.38,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We never see you here on weekdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:52.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:55.17,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, can I play Tsuboguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.75,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.51,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Total fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:06.00,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Public schools are supposed to be co-ed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.64,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but they added classes aimed at boys \Nand now it's almost a boys' school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:13.21,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboguchi-kun got a job \Nas a high school teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:16.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but there are only eight \Ngirls in his grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:21.14,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stayed in \Nschool another year...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to stay \Nin school too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:28.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one area where \Nyou can beat Master Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:28.79,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my opponent \Nfor the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.16,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.53,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You have 15 minutes to \Nmemorize the positioning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.77,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,of the 50 cards on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.16,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really memorizing \Nthe positions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.44,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:56.57,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any pictures, just words!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.66,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the cards on the other \Nside are upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.04,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:09.03,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:18.42,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:27.70,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}As my love first came to realization,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.70,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,How do they move so fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.90,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, she said something \Nabout unique syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.14,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we have to memorize the \Npoems and their unique syllables?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:38.28,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The night breaks to day, \Nand day turns to night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.03,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.11,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.03,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is someone like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.37,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.22,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's making a totally one-sided attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.71,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And he's aggressive about sending cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.54,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.53,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I have to memorize the positions again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.50,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving another card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.52,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.27,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A house left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.94,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make every second count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.94,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.09,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching them play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.07,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you're interested in joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.83,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:26.42,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to distract the \Nplayers, so let's talk over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.26,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, th-that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.70,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:34.37,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's so fun about karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.87,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.41,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you can't \Nknow until you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.42,obviously,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Obviously
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.09,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,And you still won't \Nunderstand after you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.64,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I've been playing for 45 years \Nand I still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.65,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:50.10,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been able to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.64,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.66,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.02,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, help me clear the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.15,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what are you working on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:09.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.85,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.85,Chiha-main,Chito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.17,Chiha-main,Chito,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.80,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.78,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.14,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:37.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you always come early to \Nclean up the room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about not noticing sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.07,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.97,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I only clean when I notice it's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just realized that I've only \Ndone quick, easy cleanups...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.33,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.38,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Use dry paper towels \Nto wipe tatami mats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.06,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Or a rag that's been wrung dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.53,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Never underestimate the \Ndamage water can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.52,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to help clean, \NI'll teach you the basics!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.79,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The first-years are arriving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.10,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of your own \Nresponsibilities, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.72,handwriting,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,New T-Shirts\N\NVictory or Bust           Mizusawa Power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.90,handwriting,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,National Number One       World Number One
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.78,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We lost so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:37.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I got carried away and took \Nall 100 cards during the Genpei match?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.00,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to use this \None week trial period
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.65,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to check out the other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.72,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.38,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.40,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to know \Nhow fun karuta is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.97,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but it's so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.06,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san?  What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.80,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Are you thinking \Nabout the karuta club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.83,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.  Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.61,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-senpai won't be there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.69,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving on to another target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.90,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Tajima-kun in class 2 is pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.59,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't that serious \Nabout Mashima-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.85,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We were just going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.28,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.43,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think karuta would be so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.04,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to work that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.17,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.83,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,We've only been friends a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.55,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,and we're already out of \Nthings to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:37.51,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what high school will \Nbe like if I don't join a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.92,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.44,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find a new boyfriend fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.27,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste time worrying about \Nfinding the hottest guy in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.11,Chiha-poem,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower has wilted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.76,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.68,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.37,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From: Kazuki\NSubject: (none)\NYo!  How you doing?\NWanna meet up if you're free?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.18,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.20,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who dumped me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.13,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's asking me out \Nwithout a single apology?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.88,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your true nature now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.37,Chiha-flashbackinternal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been able to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.47,Chiha-flashbackinternal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather choose the \Ngirl I devote myself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.32,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.45,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What?  There was only one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:36.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last new member, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.43,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukuba from class 1-10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tsukuba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only one left, \Nso I brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.66,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:49.21,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when you take \NMashima out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.42,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it would have been the\N same if any of us taught them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.29,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to make our \Nschool a karuta powerhouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.47,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  None of us were \Ndreaming that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.61,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I didn't want \Nto let Chihaya teach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.39,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so bad for the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.62,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They don't get to make more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.79,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, nobody was in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.60,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Hanano-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.85,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.18,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.00,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you first-years are probably \Nstill learning the ropes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.85,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but would you be up for a casual match?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.76,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.03,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.38,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are a little long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.65,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I have clippers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.45,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.68,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna clip my nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.08,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I work hard to keep them nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.54,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,But you could injure your \Nopponent if you hit their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.98,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.05,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be trying that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.96,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, they won't be moving \Nthat fast, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it a shot for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.66,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:27.24,Chiha-poem,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.81,Chiha-poem,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.95,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:31.81,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.30,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have panda eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.11,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.57,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Hanano-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kana-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.71,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Are the girls going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's never a good idea \Nfor guys to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.15,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,They can be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.20,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...  Tsukuba-kun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.71,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all these hiccups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.43,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Have you learned the cards yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.10,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...  I only know twenty or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.99,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.16,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.45,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.48,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Hanano-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.99,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.86,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making sure I look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:23.75,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,A woman must always move with grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.02,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.87,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why shouldn't I make myself pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.44,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.55,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to look nice if I want a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:34.63,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's vulgar and foolish to spend \Nall your time thinking about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.56,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.86,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Hundred Poets just \Na bunch of love poems?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:48.56,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have always spent \Na lot of time on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.37,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too interested in karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.52,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm willing to work hard for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.93,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm \Nafter Mashima-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.03,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.51,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She's seriously crazy about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.04,crazy,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Crazy\Nabout\Nkaruta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.02,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san, you haven't \Nfinished changing yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.24,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to start practice soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.63,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.39,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need makeup when \Nyou're only in high school—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.04,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, this is just a little mascara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.10,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of my identity now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.10,left,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She'd fix her mascara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.10,right,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,even in a fire
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.68,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She'd fix her mascara even in a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.44,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,These are the Hokkaido cards \NI mentioned yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.86,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,These are cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:44.06,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was in Hokkaido through middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.77,Chiha-overlap,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,They're real wood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.28,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,This is known as "Second Verse Karuta."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.83,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've heard of that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:53.05,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's where the reader skips \Nstraight to the second verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.33,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.00,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.52,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,So I've only memorized \Nthe second verses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.89,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Second Verse Karuta is usually
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.70,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,played in the form of \Nthree-on-three team matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.63,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in Hokkaido, I played all \Nthe time with my three brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.77,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,My team was undefeated \Nin local tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.29,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that everyone on the mainland \Nplays First Verse Karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.43,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to become \Ngood at that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.33,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Master, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.15,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's how good I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.97,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,These first-years are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.60,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.35,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You might have been good \Nat Second Verse Karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.99,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but the rules for competitive \Nkaruta are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.74,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a thorough \Nlecture, so take some notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:44.05,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-senpai, what's \Nyour rank or grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.89,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a first grade in Class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.60,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.30,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about Mashima-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  I'm in Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.68,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want Mashima-senpai to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.31,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.48,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.26,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.29,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The first-years can play each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But he's experienced, so all the more \Nreason to start with the basics...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.03,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.95,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being realistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.13,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to waste \Ntoo much energy when
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.36,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the prelims are coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:21.95,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.06,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work really, really hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.88,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,so I get good fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:29.33,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring,\N now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.72,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this doesn't take long,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.67,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,since I get to be with \NMashima-senpai on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.98,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The same problems keep cropping up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:37.08,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring,\N now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.15,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The mood is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.51,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.73,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,...so focused on the first-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:43.68,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The storm will soon carry \Nme to the afterlife,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.68,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Um.  Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.36,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Which one was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.44,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,so I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.67,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Tsukuba-kun's left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.70,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,None are left who know me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.95,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Takasogo pines...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He's using both hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,And he's using his left hand to guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.75,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.75,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The next one will be mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.98,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.98,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's slamming the floor to \Nintimidate his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.03,handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.70,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Second Verse Karuta is \Ncompletely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:15.47,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I know that my heart is all aflutter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:19.77,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and by no fault of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,His hand moved straight to the card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He has strong fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:32.82,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,...are wet with dew
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:39.50,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So the flower has wilted during the long \Nspring rains, just as my beauty has faded
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.74,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.13,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Trim your nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:50.98,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:51.72,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see how strong \NTsukuba-kun's fingers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If you hit him, you'll tear off your nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.44,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Tear it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.48,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm not going to \Ntry that hard at karuta—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.48,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:07.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You were happy about taking \Nyour first card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start moving faster and \Nfaster to take cards, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:14.21,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, how about your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.46,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Just trim your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.36,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.52,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:21.73,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I already said that I joined this \Nclub to be with Mashima-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.97,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,not to play karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.59,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.33,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.50,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.51,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.11,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.75,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's made it clear that she \Ndoesn't want to play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.20,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:43.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I collapsed and had to forfeit \Nlast year during the national championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent every day wondering \Nwhat would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.28,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,if we had one more member.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We finally have new members...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ignore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.21,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.43,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.80,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.67,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.73,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.50,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You can launch yourself \Nlike a catapult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.89,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see how strong \NTsukuba-kun's fingers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.41,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-senpai complimented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukuba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.09,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Class A, and I have \Nthe most experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.81,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.11,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:43.20,shojo,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Only \Nlikes \Nattractive \Npeople
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.06,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Don't groan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.28,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.91,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.50,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.78,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the basics, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.85,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're only allowed to use one \Nhand in competitive karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.48,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's against the rules \Nto use both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.93,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Are you right-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.63,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the proper \Nright-handed form, so copy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.76,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.89,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Move your right leg back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.34,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Bend over a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:03.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Your head's crossing the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.35,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.35,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,None of us blamed Ayase
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.54,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,for what happened at the \Ntournament last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.79,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,because we all knew that she \Nwas the one who hurt the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.53,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become as good as you were
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.78,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at Second Verse Karuta, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.22,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a good player.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.79,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll make you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.79,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We finally have new members...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ignore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.30,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.10,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.08,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, so come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.15,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.69,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.25,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,He knows now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:59.18,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-senpai knows how I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.29,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.66,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,You think love is foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:06.66,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here to mock me, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:14.03,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when you said
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.52,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that Hundred Poets was\N a bunch of love poems,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.42,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I had to admit you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.81,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We share the same feelings \Nthat they did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.08,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,However, Hundred Poets \Nis an anthology of poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.33,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Their poems are still known \Na thousand years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.99,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,because they expressed their \Nfeelings and techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.78,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in adherence to the 31 syllables rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.70,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings expressed are \Ndependent on the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.85,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that \Nthe president knows your
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.01,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,true feelings after hearing \Nthat little outburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.37,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.22,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.47,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, so let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.92,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.09,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.95,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.93,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Can you teach me how to put on mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.25,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Since I only have three eyelashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.82,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.15,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I think crying in embarrassment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.72,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,is a sign of a beautiful soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.00,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:35.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We still have some time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Up for a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.84,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is it okay if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.06,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I do some studying instead \Nof playing a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.77,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't memorized \Nall of the poems yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.00,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings expressed are \Ndependent on the rules.
